The First Session of the Second Forum of International Finance and Frontier Technology of the International Investment Alliance for Renewable Energy was held on Feb 17th in Beijing. Participants had in-depth exchanges and discussions on topics such as the development hot spots of the new energy industry, the trend and application of cutting-edge technologies, and green finance. At the sideline of the forum, CGTN spoke with Song Hailiang, Chairman of China Energy Engineering Group. Here's what he said about the integration of green development and digital technology.